{"tid":614822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿伯去海水浴場不游泳　只看正妹兩腿間風景","createTime":"2018-04-03T00:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T04:07:52.000Z","uid":72009,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"db2ac8eda4967ba56756163c903f2bb277199353","tid":614822,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T00:56:35.000Z","msg":"阿伯到海水浴場玩，沒有打算下水游泳，只一直盯著前方比基尼正妹的兩腿間看。<br />\n據俄羅斯《Made in CCCP》指出，有網友在網路上分享影片，地點是在俄羅斯一處的海水浴場，一對老夫老妻到此遊玩，妻子面向海邊看風景，丈夫則是拍在墊子上往前看，不過他視線前方，恰好有一位比基尼妹M字開腿，旁邊民眾發現到阿伯的意圖後發生大笑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20180402/1327428\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20180402%2F1327428&d=stdLRpnMc9xOK92dHEH%2BLIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=c7730e86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20180402%2F1327428&h=6df4c19e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20180402/1327428</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180402/640_967de758534bd2477b1f7b8b8b9cf8d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180402%2F640_967de758534bd2477b1f7b8b8b9cf8d9.jpg&h=4ca2338c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c334d2e0e70047fb6ff26bb099295b6ac8a0f5a5","tid":614822,"uid":42453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T00:57:31.000Z","msg":"生活態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23ffcb171a7fe7224eccf6c5203f6a0d0e4d69f","tid":614822,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T00:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1744b1d30ee34fe30f041815bba58fbb4652d8d7","tid":614822,"uid":51932,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03